short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Serp Analyzer provides additional information about Google search results for those interested in SEO.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Serp Analyzer allows you to have various information about a search results page:

- Ranking of each domain
- Access the top 100
- Export all ranked URLs
- Export People Also Ask
